3. In-Game Economy Features
The Game includes several economic features that must be understood before engaging in play:

In-Game Taxes: The Game includes an in-game tax system. Players are required to pay taxes using only in-game currency. These taxes apply to in-game transactions and services.

Bankruptcy System: The Game includes a bankruptcy feature, where players may go bankrupt based on their in-game financial decisions.

Gas Station Theme: The Game is set in a gas station simulation. All interactions and gameplay revolve around this theme.

